title: The Draymond Green Show - Championship Reaction From TD Garden

description:
Draymond Green is joined by Klay Thompson, Andre Iguodala, and Gary Payton II to celebrate and react to the Golden State Warriors winning their fourth championship in the modern era. #Herd
